defter-scrolling (0.8.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Add generic Linux install and uninstall scripts
  * Auto-enable and start service in install script
  * Improved scrolling algorithm based on tractrix curves
  * Support for horizontal/biaxial scrolling
  * Configurable activation buttons with fallback support

